<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在石头上刻字，好厉害啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算用这种方式也要记录下来的事，<delay20 />
到底<delay8 />是什么样的事呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好漂亮啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和它的名字一样，<delay20 />
充满神圣感，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说的<delay8 />就是这样的作品吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个人<delay8 />到底在看什么呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />观察作品中人物的视线，<delay20 />
也是件挺有趣的事呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />真是的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为这幅有名的名画中的人物<delay20 />
笑容实在是太美了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就忍不住模仿起来了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">看着<delay8 />这幅动人的名画，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉心灵得到了净化呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来绘画作品对人心情的治愈效果<delay20 />
还挺不容小觑的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅<delay8 />惊人的名画<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />里面的人物看起来好像马上要冲出画布一样，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太棒了！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />如果真的冲出来了，
一定会被吓得腿软吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是个可爱的女孩子！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像小时候的我一样！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不过，<delay8 />真要比起来，<delay20 />
还是我更有气质吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅名贵的名画中的人物，<delay20 />
率领众人时的凛然姿态好棒啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有时就连自己的事<delay20 />
都不知道该如何决断呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然这幅画充满幻想色彩，<delay20 />　
但画中的花草都很逼真呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为它们看起来太过真实，<delay20 />
让人忍不住想摸一摸确认真假！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不可思议<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这画看起来绝不是明亮的感觉，<delay20 />
却会让观者感到很安心呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画看起来<delay8 />很像今天的我呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />随性悠闲地任时光流逝，<delay20 />
从这平静的表情中就能看出来！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这用色真是太有魅力了！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用这么鲜艳的色彩来描绘夜晚的景色，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人生畏的才能啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好有气势的作品啊，<delay40 />
大自然的力量，<delay8 />像这样被表现在一幅画上，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人好生感动。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这尊<delay8 />武士的雕刻<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太过逼真，<delay8 />让我禁不住担心<delay20 />
它会不会突然动起来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay8 />真是讨人喜欢的作品呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圆滚滚的造型，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也太可爱了吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">对了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人生啊，<delay20 />就是这样，<delay8 />
会与各种烦恼相伴。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以说，<delay8 />像这样纠结于一件事，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得反而对身体不好呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这件作品<delay8 />是你捐赠的吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对艺术感兴趣，是件很好的事情呢！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你让我欣赏到了好的作品。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>